gui.appliedenergistics2.ChargedQuartz: Charged Certus Quartz is crafted by inserting an uncharged Certus Quartz Crystal into the Charger, and powering it.
gui.appliedenergistics2.ChargedQuartzFin: Charged Certus Quartz can be found in world semi rarely, it appears similar to normal Certus Quartz, except it sparkles.
gui.appliedenergistics2.CopyModeDesc: Controls if the contents of the configuration pane are cleared when you remove the cell.
gui.appliedenergistics2.InterfaceTermina: Show Or Hide on Interface Terminal.
gui.appliedenergistics2.TransparentFacad: Controls visibility of facades while the network tool is on your toolbar.
gui.appliedenergistics2.validation.Numbe: Please enter a number greater than or equal to %d
gui.appliedenergistics2.inWorldCraftingP: Crafting Presses are found in the center of meteorites which can be found in around the world, they can be located by using a meteorite compass.
gui.appliedenergistics2.inWorldFluix: Drop 1 Charged Certus Quartz + 1 Nether Quartz + Redstone Dust into a puddle next to one another and wait a moment to receive 2 Fluix Crystals.
gui.appliedenergistics2.inWorldPurificat: Drop a Certus Quartz Seed made from Certus Quartz Dust and Sand into a puddle of water; to make the process faster add Crystal Growth Accelerators.
Drop a Fluix Seed made from Fluix Dust and Sand into a puddle of water; to make the process faster add Crystal Growth Accelerators.
Drop a Nether Quartz Seed made from Nether Quartz Dust and Sand into a puddle of water; to make the process faster add Crystal Growth Accelerators.
gui.appliedenergistics2.inWorldSingulari: To create drop 1 Singularity and 1 Ender Dust and cause an explosion within range of the items.
gui.appliedenergistics2.security.build.t: User can modify the physical structure of the network, and make configuration changes.
gui.appliedenergistics2.security.craft.t: User can initiate new crafting jobs.
gui.appliedenergistics2.security.extract: User is allowed to remove items from storage.
User is allowed to store new items into storage.
gui.appliedenergistics2.security.securit: User can access and modify the security terminal of the network.

gui.tooltips.appliedenergistics2.Blockin: Do not push crafting items if inventory contains items.

gui.tooltips.appliedenergistics2.CraftOn: Do not use stocked items, only craft items while exporting.
gui.tooltips.appliedenergistics2.EmitLev: Emit when levels are above or equal to limit.
Emit when levels are below limit.
gui.tooltips.appliedenergistics2.EmitWhe: Emit Redstone while item is crafting.

Yes: Fluids that cannot be extracted will be visible.
